name: NEVER HOME [intro.]
description:
[i've never been able to tell which way home is.] 

================================================= 
NEVER HOME- a series by CIPOTE
================================================= 

This series explores the space between borders. An invisible area occupied by the children of migration. Can you ever be Home if you belong to no land? Without land to grow roots in, will you create, or destroy? 

[1280x960]
